articles.title: Paclitaxel compromises nuclear integrity in interphase through SUN2-mediated cytoskeletal coupling.
articles.summary: Paclitaxel disrupts cancer cell nuclear integrity by altering lamin A/C protein levels and organization through SUN2-mediated cytoskeletal interactions during interphase.

articles.title: Endobronchial ultrasound-guided mediastinal biopsies for the diagnosis of mediastinal diseases: A network meta-analysis.
articles.summary: A network meta-analysis shows endobronchial ultrasound-guided biopsies effectively diagnose mediastinal diseases, particularly in lung cancer staging.
